# Cloudflare Pages redirects file.
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
#
# Intentionally empty of rules. This app uses HashRouter (routes are
# /#/dashboard, not /dashboard), so every in-app navigation already
# resolves to the single static index.html file without any
# server-side rewriting — there's no path that needs a SPA fallback
# rule here. (An earlier `/*  /index.html  200` catch-all was removed:
# it wasn't needed for HashRouter, and it also triggers a known
# Wrangler local-dev false-positive "infinite loop" warning —
# https://github.com/cloudflare/workers-sdk/issues/11824 — even though
# Cloudflare's production edge handles the rule correctly.)
